high_descs: Go to the kitchen counter on the right.
Pick up the paring knife in front of the bread.
Go around the counter to the white round table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn left to go to the gray trash can next to the counter.
Place the knife inside the trashcan.
Turn around and go back to the white round table.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Go to the refrigerator on the opposite side of the kitchen.
Place the sliced tomato in the refrigerator to chill it and take it out.
Turn right to go to the trashcan at the end of the counter.
Place the tomato slice in the trashcan.
anns.task_desc: Throw out the paring knife and chilled slice of tomato.
